# X-and-O /\ Tic-Tac-Toe
Simple Tic Tac Toe game
A two player game of Tic Tac Toe also known as X and O.
To play the game kindly follow the following steps:

1.Each player takes turns in clicking a square. When a square is clicked either an X or an O is drawn depending on the player playing.
2.The first player to have either O's or X's in a horizontal, vertical or slanting 3 adjacent line wins.
3.If the 9 tiles are filled without a winner the game declares a draw.
4.When the game ends it gives you an option to restart the game click.
